title: Consumed.The.Real.Restaurant.Business.S01E01.WS.DSR.x264-NY2.mp4
description:
CNBC's Consumed is a docu-series that takes you behind the scenes of three very different restaurants in the ultra-competitive New York food scene. The series chronicles their every struggle and occasional triumph.

Eating may be a pleasure but making it in the New York restaurant world is serious business. However this is more than a show about restaurants, it is a show where restaurant owners are chasing their slice of the American dream.




Consumed: The Real Restaurant Business - Season 1, Episode 1



Eat or Get Eaten

The premiere of a series focusing on three New York City restaurants begins with a trendy meatball chain looking to expand; a Harlem eatery searching for new ways to grow; and a family-run Italian establishment in the Bronx trying to attract customers.




Original Air Date: 13-May-2015
